.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-BALANCE-RATIO-MIN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-balance-ratio-min \- FEAT-3001 peer-balance-ratio-min
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-balance-ratio-min
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the minimum balance ratio across peers for the lightning CLI (FEAT-3001).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBbalance_ratio_min_peer\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
